### OUTPUT REQUIREMENTS
1. Briefly analyze how this feature maps to the 5 layers before coding.
2. Provide production-ready C# 8.0+ code.
3. Add summary XML comments explaining the "Why" behind the architectural choices in the code.
4. Output only the code blocks and the brief analysis. No generic disclaimers.